The paper discusses the application of deep learning techniques in point cloud semantic segmentation, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses traditional and advanced techniques used for point cloud segmentation, which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the acquisition and evolution of 3D point clouds, which could fall under graphics (cs.GR).
